{"tid":1277530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［衝突背後］香港人最需要突破的，是心中的那一道防線。","createTime":"2019-07-02T08:09:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T10:38:52.000Z","uid":35699,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"299fe2935d8e78f5b3ee82a97963aae75c662269","tid":1277530,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:09:01.000Z","msg":"昨日看到的畫面悍勇非常，將梁天琦的「以武制暴」、「以死相搏」活生生呈現香港當中。梁天琦當年的進步思想，除了抗爭方式的想像之外，還有對於香港前途的刻畫。<br />\n<br />\n梁天琦當年對香港前途的願景：<br />\n「港獨係實現自治嘅方式」<br />\n「無論係港獨，一國兩制又好，咩都好，其實真正想要嘅係自治，而港獨係一種實現香港自治嘅方式，which is 我哋而家係冇嘅。」<br />\n「（自治）現時未可行，將來絕對有機會。」<br />\n<br />\n梁天琦的未竟之路，究竟香港人會否一起走完呢？<br />\n請由今日起衝破心裏面的防線。"},{"pid":"4d16b3a34c5aeac251c25ea6dba4f063db1fc45c","tid":1277530,"uid":35699,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:10:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20160217/large/17la1p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20160217%2Flarge%2F17la1p2.jpg&h=ccb9e66e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4c134a2dddf78cafa0c375c7c488544445d8566","tid":1277530,"uid":35699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:15:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hongkongpignews/videos/959519860769090/UzpfSTE1NDY5MjU0ODIyMjgwMjU6MjM3NDU3MzEyMjc5NjU4Ng/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhongkongpignews%2Fvideos%2F959519860769090%2FUzpfSTE1NDY5MjU0ODIyMjgwMjU6MjM3NDU3MzEyMjc5NjU4Ng%2F&d=Mrz8gheyF4cbCiJyPb%2FME5bpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=336b1b35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hongkongpignews/videos/959519860769090/UzpfSTE1NDY5MjU0ODIyMjgwMjU6MjM3NDU3MzEyMjc5NjU4Ng/</a>"},{"pid":"43793535c5f4756b596fd961e9af42196b54a7d7","tid":1277530,"uid":35699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.ne